### Gerardus 't Hooft: A Mind Carved from Theoretical Physics

In the arcane world of [Dutch names](/Dutch_name), one must be precise. The [surname](/Surname) here is 't Hooft, not merely Hooft. A small distinction, perhaps, but one that separates the signal from the noise. And Gerardus 't Hooft, a name that echoes in the hallowed halls of theoretical physics, is very much signal.

#### Gerard 't Hooft

